Package: vinylsplit
Version: 0.9.0-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Justin Pasley <you@example.com>
Installed-Size: 289
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Description: Automatically split vinyl recordings into tagged tracks
 VinylSplit analyzes a full-album recording, detects track boundaries,
 identifies tracks using AcoustID/MusicBrainz, embeds metadata and artwork,
 and exports organized FLAC files.
